snippet.title: Guild Wars 2 Living World: The Icebrood Saga Announce Trailer
snippet.description: The next Living World story, The Icebrood Saga, begins on September 17. Get access to the Icebrood Saga episodes as soon as they're live--and Guild Wars 2: Heart of Thorns for FREE--when you buy Guild Wars 2: Path of Fire. Buy now: https://buy.guildwars2.com?cid=304:5::::NA:18::84:
